{"tid":126193,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[拋磚引玉]擺低一樣你每次見到都會笑嘅嘢","createTime":"2017-02-19T07:19:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-19T09:07:59.000Z","uid":15491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6196197d48cb75d529796c6c4d4db14e26ef186f","tid":126193,"uid":15491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T07:19:40.000Z","msg":"可以係一個畫面 一樣物件 一篇潮文 咩都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大笑 傻笑 苦笑都可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/78yEO5a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F78yEO5a.jpg&h=cf7513b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/19/151753_a5371e033d4e3b329c898bf94f42824f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F19%2F151753_a5371e033d4e3b329c898bf94f42824f.jpg&h=b8079230&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17003a98a797c25755f9527dc763cbc679837a37","tid":126193,"uid":15491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T07:20:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99f8923e9cd45a5be20a77cd372fbb66dc57e34d","tid":126193,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T07:21:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/t2z95od0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ft2z95od0&h=b6746ec9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4cd1fb156f49b16d274cac3932121e08b76b2784","tid":126193,"uid":15491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T07:26:36.000Z","msg":"想當年我仲讀緊BAND 3中學<br />\n<br />\n有條MK向左走向右走狗咁向左走向右走我, 話約我隻揪<br />\n<br />\n佢以為自己有腹肌就好向左走向右走好打<br />\n<br />\n(但其實我當時己經舉左兩三年鐵,一直有飲奶粉<br />\n<br />\n不過我BULK緊, 即係夜神起義 Bane 果種大隻型<br />\n<br />\n所以D肌肉線條未現到出黎)<br />\n<br />\n我D 毒向左走向右走FD 嚇向左走向右走到標尿<br />\n<br />\n「唔好同佢打呀, 佢有腹肌架」<br />\n<br />\n「你癡左線咩, 你見唔見到佢幾咁FIT 呀」<br />\n<br />\n我心諗話你怕你嬲<br />\n<br />\n有腹肌唔等於有力量<br />\n<br />\n我笑笑口咁答應左條MK 放學去籃球場打過<br />\n<br />\nfast forward 去到決戰時間<br />\n<br />\n成班同學企哂係側邊睇<br />\n<br />\n佢就除左件校服<br />\n<br />\n成個小醜咁係到穀佢果幾舊腹肌仔<br />\n<br />\n見到成班以為佢好好打果個情景,我真係快忍不住笑<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然最後佢打到我仆街, 牙都甩埋<br />\n<br />\n但完全同腹肌冇關<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢篇潮文都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3095ee99f8db88ecb37aeac994d728c6ba47aa4a","tid":126193,"uid":12524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T09:07:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/19/170757_39e5b9ef60a70497c50592b09c87f6df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F19%2F170757_39e5b9ef60a70497c50592b09c87f6df.jpg&h=700b2aa9&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}